    "description": {
      "content": "The Card on File Data Inquiry API enables issuers and merchants to retrieve information about where a cardholder's Visa credentials are stored on file with merchants. This service helps issuers provide cardholder transparency into which merchants have their card details stored, supporting card lifecycle management and fraud prevention.\n\nContact Support:\n Name: Visa Developer Support",
      "type": "text/plain"
    }
